cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper belongs to the field of natural language processing (NLP) and specifically focuses on enhancing the performance of LSTM models for text categorization tasks. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with information retrieval and classification, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) sub-categories.
